sql_query.sql:
SELECT "tag_groups".* FROM "tag_groups" WHERE ((
  id IN (SELECT tag_group_id FROM category_tag_groups WHERE category_id IN (1,197,198))
  OR
  id NOT IN (SELECT tag_group_id FROM category_tag_groups)
)
AND id IN (SELECT tag_group_id FROM tag_group_permissions WHERE group_id = 0)
) ORDER BY name ASC
SELECT "tags".* FROM "tags" INNER JOIN "tag_group_memberships" ON "tags"."id" = "tag_group_memberships"."tag_id" WHERE "tag_group_memberships"."tag_group_id" = 27 AND "tags"."target_tag_id" IS NULL
SELECT "tags".* FROM "tags" WHERE (tags.id NOT IN (SELECT tag_id FROM tag_group_memberships)) AND (tags.topic_count > 0)
